text: The Pines is a locality in the Toowoomba Region, Queensland, Australia. In the , The Pines had a population of 48 people. == Geography == The land use is rural residential with large acreage blocks. == Education == There are no schools in The Pines. The nearest primary and secondary school to Year 10 is in Millmerran and the nearest secondary school to Year 12 in is Pittsworth. == References == Category:Toowoomba Region Category:Localities in Queensland
title: The Pines, Queensland
